    "• Data Accessibility: The design of our framework enables domain teams to easily share their data products and make them easily accessible to other business domains.",
    "Thus, it improves data collaboration and sharing, and eliminates redundancy and duplication of efforts.",
    "Using our framework, datasets will no longer be stored in isolated silos.",
    "Every domain has a replica of the datasets catalog and may easily view them and request access to any dataset by issuing smart contract transactions.",
    "• Transparency: Blockchain, by design, promotes transparency within a data mesh."
